OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There has been a "massive shift" in the
OL,6, way we do our grocery shopping since   
OL,7, the pandemic, according to analyst firm
OL,8, Kantar.                                
OL,10,FAmong the changes, shoppers now visit  
OL,11,Fthe supermarket less often, spend more 
OL,12,Fon own-label goods and are turning to  
OL,13,Floyalty schemes to get discounts.      
OL,15,FThe cost-of-living crisis has helped   
OL,16,Fdrive the changes, as food prices soar.
OL,18,FBut trends such as the rise of the     
OL,19,Fdiscounters Aldi and Lidl go back      
OL,20,Ffurther.                               
